						<div class="postbody">Yes, they're either both on or both off, more or less.<br /><br />The halt flag represents a delay of action until the next sequencer clock. It corresponds to a real hardware function of some sort, but I have no idea how it's actually implemented. I dunno what the best name for these things is, I've just left it as is when making revisions to the wiki. Control seems an okay name for the bit, especially since there's that layer of indirection (represented by the internal &quot;halt&quot; flag).</div>

